original_title: Hyaena: Queen Of The Masai Mara
overview: This is the unusual portrait of a much maligned hunter, the hyena - a dramatic story built around the competition for prey and territory and the fight for survival. The setting is Kenya's legendary Masai Mara where lions, cheetahs and other top predators compete for survival.
title: Hyaena: Queen Of The Masai Mara
